Cookies & Corks Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
Wine.com brings to you a unique tasting experience from Cookies & Corks - all natural, gourmet, sweet and savory cookies crafted to pair with wines. These decadent cookies contain distinctive ingredients like espresso, parmesan, thyme, dark chocolate, lemon, rosemary and sea salt - all perfect complements to wine varietals. We encourage you or your gift recipients to have fun pairing these cookies with two wines, the Joel Gott Blend No. 815 Cabernet Sauvignon and the Nino Franco Rustico Prosecco. But no matter how you mix and match, a dynamic combination of flavors shows up to entertain and delight you.

Wine Gift Includes:

    • Joel Gott Blend No. 815 Cabernet Sauvignon:
      This Cabernet Sauvignon offers engaging and layered aromas of blackberry and dark blum with hints of spice, cedar, and vanilla. The polished tannins and velvety texture lead to an elegant and long finish.

    • Nino Franco Rustico Prosecco
      This sparkling Rustico Prosecco is unquestionably the world's finest value in a high quality, Champagne look-alike. It offers gorgeously elegant, fresh, lively fruit, notes of bread dough and citrus, and persistent effervescence.

    • Cookies & Corks Red Wine Pairing Box This box contains fifteen bite-sized cookies, created to pair with different red wine varietals. Box includes five Espresso Chocolate Peanut Butter, five White Cheddar Rosemary, and five Shortbread cookies.

    • Cookies & Corks Sparkling Wine Pairing Box This box contains fifteen bite-sized cookies, created to pair with different sparkling wine varietals. Box includes five Zesty Lemon, five Parmesan Thyme, and five Sea Salt Chocolate Oatmeal.

    • Festive greet sheet

    Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

    Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

    Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

Riedel 'O' - Set of 2 Viognier/Chardonnay
List.Description:
This Riedel glass series has something missing; there is no stem or base. Riedel 'O' is the innovative take on the wine tumbler, the designs of which are based on the benchmark shapes of the Riedel Vinum. These are the ideal glasses for every day use and for every occasion; they are fun and feel good to hold.

The 'O' series is a lead free machine blown series, and is dishwasher safe. The 'O' Viognier/Chardonnay tumbler is ideally suited to showcase the best characteristics of medium to full bodied white wines such as Viognier, white Burgundy and Old World Chardonnay.

Tumblers hold 11 1/4 oz and stand 3 7/8" high.
Sold in a boxed set of 2.

Wine sold separately.

Bountiful Vineyard Wine Gift Basket
List.Description:
This basket overflows with wine country-inspired treats paired with three bottles of delicious wine: Parducci Chardonnay from Mendocino County, Raymond Field Blend R Collection from Sonoma County, and Guenoc Victorian Claret from the North Coast region of California.

Wine Gift Basket Includes:

  • Parducci Chardonnay:
    Honoring the rich heritage of the Chardonnay grape, Parducci selects individually vinified small lots of this premium varietal to blend a wine of bold, lively character and balanced flavors. This Chardonnay has crisp, clean flavors of apple, pear and tropical fruits.

  • Raymond Field Blend R Collection:
    This field blend displays aromas of ripe red fruit and exotic spices. Flavors of tangy raspberries, fresh-picked strawberries, and red currant coat the palate with a delightfully rich flavor profile.

  • Guenoc Victorian Claret:
    This Claret is a complex blend of award winning wines. Dark ruby in color, the wine has a wonderful fruity nose bringing in black cherry, plum, and blueberry aromas.
